{"tid":1624172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為天琦刑期上訴眾籌 ！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T03:26:43.000Z","uid":10973,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"acd9fba59aa94faed2b01877e85cdf1003f1bf3c","tid":1624172,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:07:50.000Z","msg":"【為天琦刑期上訴眾籌】<br />\n<br />\n各位愛護天琦的香港人：<br />\n<br />\n相信大家一直有關注天琦的消息，他的刑期上訴聆訊將於10月9日在高等法院審理。天琦的家人及好友慎重權衡後，決定聘請資深大律師代表天琦上訴。由於所費不菲，我們無奈之下發起眾籌，冀望聚沙成塔，目標金額為35萬，誠盼各位可與天琦同行。<br />\n<br />\n義工小組 敬上<br />\n<br />\n眾籌連結：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=ae427fa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\n眾籌目標：35萬港元（包括平台手續費6.9%，達標即止，為免加重大家的負擔，我們希望每人捐款不多於1000元）<br />\n<br />\n【Call for funding for Edward Leung's sentence appeal】<br />\n<br />\nDear fellow Hong Kongers,<br />\n<br />\nAs you all know, Edward&rsquo;s sentence appeal hearing will be held in the High Court on October 9.  After much thought and consideration, we decided to hire a senior counsel to represent Edward in the appeal case.  In order to cover the significant legal costs, we would like to raise HK$350,000 through crowdfunding.  We sincerely hope that you could give Edward a hand and thank you in advance for your contribution.<br />\n<br />\nWith warmest regards,<br />\nEdward&rsquo;s Volunteer Team<br />\n<br />\nCrowdfunding link: <a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fedwardleungappeal%2F&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqoZnnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=ae427fa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/edwardleungappeal/</a><br />\nCrowdfunding target: HK$350,000 &ndash; including the platform handling fee of 6.9% and will end once the target is met. We advise that each person shall donate no more than HK$1,000.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjyBW5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjyBW5d.jpg&h=9eb200f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9/10 高院</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9270a68adcb6dcb5d354a5b6c90a6f94b8d0826","tid":1624172,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510073487a553a9d0f384979ee943d7e9dfe463d","tid":1624172,"uid":269910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca18bfb88e338f073972ce90568c98ca34acfa6","tid":1624172,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9270a68adcb6dcb5d354a5b6c90a6f94b8d0826","tid":1624172,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"9/10 高院"},{"pid":"1e442c2a649cd49002f2c878441921f85cc1b97d","tid":1624172,"uid":10973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"510073487a553a9d0f384979ee943d7e9dfe463d","tid":1624172,"uid":269910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"9/10 高院"},{"pid":"6eddbf1216d9566064b02fc10e9ad98e55500668","tid":1624172,"uid":20922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,